 placement of <i>every</i> player on the field...

10:52.670 --> 10:55.010
You're right. It's crazy talk.

10:55.780 --> 10:57.940
But I've been thinkin'...

10:58.270 --> 11:02.050
The speed of Ashito's progress is no joke.

11:03.780 --> 11:09.600
His basics are laughable, but once he 
gets somethin' down, he owns that skill.

11:09.600 --> 11:11.690
He's able to put it to use, I mean.

11:11.960 --> 11:17.820
No one masters a technique that fast. 
Seems like he has some kind of...

11:18.120 --> 11:20.700
...extraordinary instinctual ability.

11:21.240 --> 11:28.450
