as they can. They're totally going for the draw.

13:11.010 --> 13:13.100
Just make the substitution already, you—

13:14.770 --> 13:18.030
<i>There's no time left. 
Maybe just enough for one more play.</i>

13:19.220 --> 13:20.060
You...

13:22.900 --> 13:24.850
You need to calm down.

13:29.540 --> 13:30.790
I'm...

13:31.530 --> 13:32.390
I'm sorry.

13:43.070 --> 13:45.180
I'll score a goal for you.

13:48.750 --> 13:53.060
Aoi! I'll take the throw-in. 
I need you up front. Go up front.

13:57.030 --> 13:59.870
<i>Triangles. Eye contact.</i>

14:00.810 --> 14:04.280
<i>I learned a different side 
to soccer, and it's awesome.</i>

14:05.270 --> 14:09.030
<i>Use the players around you, 
and let the team score.</i>

14:09.630 --> 14:11.780
<i>But that's just where it starts.</i>

14:12.110 --> 14:13.730
<i>I'm going to score.</i>

14:15.150 --> 14:17.890
<i>I'll take it one step further and use my head.</i>

14:26.050 --> 14:27.800
Everyone on offense!

14:33.310 --> 14:35.580
Don't look so anxious! Defend the goal!

14:35.580 --> 14:37.810
<i>Defend the goal? But how?</i>

14:37.810 --> 14:40.310
<i>Do we stick more players on those three?</i>

14:40.650 --> 14:43.060
<i>But we tried that already!</i>

14:43.060 --> 14:46.500
<i>We ended up leaving that 
midfielder unmarked and he scored.</i>

14:46.500 --> 14:50.820
<i>Which means they can coordinate 
a move with any player on the field!</i>

14:50.840 --> 14:54.650
<i>Who do we pick up?
 Who are we supposed to mark?</i>

14:55.080 --> 14:56.580
I'm coming for you!

14:58.080 --> 15:02.450
<i>He's the one who started this. His play 
suddenly changed and everything went south!</i>

15:02.450 --> 15:06.350
<i>We should have taken him out sooner!</i>

15:06.840 --> 15:08.110
Asari!

15:08.970 --> 15:09.950
Play on!

15:10.590 --> 15:12.380
Don't get drawn out! Stay back!

15:13.460 --> 15:17.420
Their tactic is to draw you out, 
so stay put in front of the goal!

15:21.010 --> 15:24.980
All I need to do... is bring myself.

15:26.840 --> 15:30.230
All I need to do is bring myself.

