<i>The right side's totally open.</i>

15:57.170 --> 15:58.430
<i>Yes, it is.</i>

15:59.450 --> 16:02.260
<i>How come no one's going over there?</i>

16:02.810 --> 16:06.530
<i>It's clear to us because 
we're seeing it from above.</i>

16:06.530 --> 16:09.400
<i>The view at ground level is very limited.</i>

16:09.810 --> 16:13.410
<i>So don't be mad at the players.</i>

16:13.980 --> 16:19.760
<i>Isn't it like a dream, being able to see and 
know where the players are from above,</i>

16:20.120 --> 16:23.770
<i>as if you're a bird in flight,
 circling over the field?</i>

16:24.300 --> 16:25.770
<i>But it's </i>not<i> a dream.</i>

16:26.180 --> 16:32.820
